    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your Bladesong beautifully weaves magic with melee combat. While your Bladesong is active, you gain the follow benefits.</p><p><strong>Extra Damage.</strong> You can add your Intelligence modifier (minimum of +1) to the damage of your melee weapon attacks while your Bladesong is active.</p><p><strong>Arcane-Boosted Attacks.</strong> Whenever you maintain Concentration on a Wizard spell of 1st level or higher, creatures you hit with a melee weapon attack takes extra damage equal to 1d6 + the spell's level. The extra damage is the same type dealt by the weapon or the spell you are concentrating on if it has a damage type (your choice).</p>",
